  'Description': '{"entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"","text":"Interested in the field of Machine Learning?\\u00a0Then this course is for you!This course has been designed by two professional Data Scientists so that we can share our knowledge and help you learn complex theory,\\u00a0algorithms, and coding libraries in a simple way.We will walk you step-by-step into the World of Machine Learning. With every tutorial, you will develop new skills and improve your understanding of this challenging yet lucrative sub-field of Data Science.This course is\\u00a0fun and exciting, but at the same time, we dive deep into Machine Learning. It is structured the following way:Part 1 - Data PreprocessingPart 2 - Regression: Simple Linear Regression, Multiple Linear Regression,\\u00a0Polynomial\\u00a0Regression,\\u00a0SVR, Decision Tree Regression,\\u00a0Random Forest RegressionPart 3 - Classification: Logistic Regression, K-NN, SVM, Kernel SVM, Naive Bayes, Decision Tree Classification,\\u00a0Random\\u00a0Forest ClassificationPart 4 - Clustering: K-Means,\\u00a0Hierarchical ClusteringPart 5 - Association Rule Learning: Apriori,\\u00a0EclatPart 6 - Reinforcement Learning:\\u00a0Upper Confidence Bound,\\u00a0Thompson SamplingPart 7 - Natural Language Processing: Bag-of-words model\\u00a0and\\u00a0algorithms for NLPPart 8 - Deep Learning: Artificial Neural Networks,\\u00a0Convolutional Neural NetworksPart 9 - Dimensionality Reduction: PCA, LDA, Kernel PCAPart 10 - Model Selection & Boosting: k-fold Cross Validation, Parameter Tuning, Grid Search,\\u00a0XGBoostMoreover, the course is packed with practical exercises that are based on real-life\\u00a0examples. So not only will you learn the theory, but you will also get some hands-on practice building your own models.And as a bonus, this course includes both\\u00a0Python and R\\u00a0code templates which you can download and use on your own projects.Important updates (June 2020):CODES ALL UP TO DATEDEEP LEARNING CODED IN TENSORFLOW 2.0TOP GRADIENT BOOSTING MODELS INCLUDING XGBOOST AND EVEN CATBOOST!","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]}',
